<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢١٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> سَلمَة بن الْحجَّاج<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عِكْرِمَة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الْأسود بن سِنَان.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كناه يحيى بن سعيد.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١٢١٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> سَلمَة بن عَلْقَمَة التَّمِيمِي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> نَافِع.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> شُعْبَة وَغَيره.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>كناه شباب الْعُصْفُرِي.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أخبرنَا أَحْمد بن مهْرَان الْفَارِسِي , وَأحمد بن<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عُثْمَان الْأَبْهَرِيّ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَا:</span> ثَنَا مُوسَى بن زَكَرِيَّا ,<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>ثَنَا شباب بِهَذَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٢٢٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> مُبشر بن عبيد الْمُقْرِئ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>الْحِمصِي.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سُلَيْمَان الْأَعْمَش , وَأبي عَمْرو بن<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>الْعَلَاء.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو حَيْوَة شُرَيْح بن يزِيد , وَبَقِيَّة بن<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>الْوَلِيد وكناه.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>١٢٢١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> وَيُقَال: أَبُو عُبَيْدَة:<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ , عبد الْوَاحِد بن زِيَاد.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>أخبرنَا إِبْرَاهِيم بن مُحَمَّد النَّيْسَابُورِي، ثَنَا مُحَمَّد بن إِسْحَاق الثَّقَفِيّ، ثَنَا قُتَيْبَة بن سعيد، ثَنَا أَبُو بشر عبد الْوَاحِد بن زِيَاد.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>١٢٢٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> أدهم بن عَليّ السدُوسِي.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> مطرف بن عبد الله الشخير ,<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>وَجَابِر بن زيد.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> شُعْبَة , وَابْن علية.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب بن يُوسُف ,<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span><a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>سَمِعت عَبَّاس بن مُحَمَّد الدوري ,<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>سَمِعت يحيى بن معِين ,<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> أدهم<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>السدُوسِي كنيته أَبُو بشر.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>١٢٢٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> حَوْشَب بن مُسلم<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> الْحسن.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>كناه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>١٢٢٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> شُعَيْب بن أبي حَمْزَة<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>الْحِمصِي , وَهُوَ ابْن دِينَار.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> الزُّهْرِيّ وَنَافِع , وَمُحَمّد بن<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>الْمُنْكَدر.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> ابْنه بشر , وَبَقِيَّة بن الْوَلِيد بن<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>مُسلم وَغَيرهم.<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>أخبرنَا الْحسن بن مَنْصُور الإِمَام بحمص , ثَنَا<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>مُحَمَّد بن الْعَبَّاس , ثَنَا أَبُو الْيَمَان الحكم ابْن<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>نَافِع , ثَنَا أَبُو بشر شُعَيْب بن أبي حَمْزَة الزُّهْرِيّ<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span><span class="c2">(ق ٥١ / أ)</span> .<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
